31:05.170 --> 31:06.740
Stop it!

31:06.750 --> 31:07.739
[Xander grunts]

31:11.830 --> 31:14.162
I'm not the risk!

31:14.170 --> 31:15.819
Okay? They're the risk!

31:25.880 --> 31:27.871
He's gonna be a problem.

31:31.290 --> 31:33.030
