It's a lot of money.

37:59.580 --> 38:00.820
What are you planning
on doing with it?

38:00.830 --> 38:02.411
Renovating your shop?

38:02.420 --> 38:04.877
I'll tell you the same thing
I told your husband.

38:04.880 --> 38:06.575
It's none of your business.

38:06.580 --> 38:07.740
Actually, it is.

38:07.750 --> 38:08.956
If you really think
about it,

38:08.960 --> 38:11.872
it's pretty unlikely that you

38:11.880 --> 38:14.030
are related to the Pownalls.

38:14.040 --> 38:17.532
My family has been in this town
a lot longer than you have,

38:17.540 --> 38:21.032
so you're not really qualified
to make such a claim.

38:21.040 --> 38:23.031
The account is mine.

38:23.040 --> 38:24.371
You have no recourse.

38:25.670 --> 38:27.206
I'm quite busy.

38:27.210 --> 38:28.370
Shall I get Scott,

38:28.380 --> 38:31.247
or will you be
exiting on your own?

38:31.250 --> 38:33.206
If you don't mind.

38:38.620 --> 38:40.747
[door opens, bell jingles]

38:40.750 --> 38:41.956
[door closes]

38:47.540 --> 38:49.371
[door opens]

38:49.380 --> 38:51.075
I think they were all drunk.

38:51.080 --> 38:53.036
I don't know,
they were barefoot,

38:53.040 --> 38:54.871
acting all weird,

38:54.880 --> 38:56.666
seemed like foreigners.

38:58.580 --> 38:59.615
How many?

38:59.620 --> 39:01.872
I don't know,
six, seven.

39:01.880 --> 39:03.609
And it was one
of the women

39:03.620 --> 39:04.450
that pushed you
to the ground?

39:04.460 --> 39:05.449
Yep.

39:05.460 --> 39:07.416
Anything else you can think of?

39:07.420 --> 39:08.489
Vehicles?

39:08.500 --> 39:10.616
Yeah, they got in a van.

39:10.620 --> 39:12.531
Uh, Pownall Seafood.

39:12.540 --> 39:13.700
[Marissa] Pownall?

39:13.710 --> 39:15.450
Ted Pownall's
got some property

39:15.460 --> 39:17.075
not too far from here.

39:17.080 --> 39:18.286
All right.

39:19.500 --> 39:21.070
[Eliza, practicing]
Hello.

39:21.080 --> 39:23.241
[Levi] Hello.

39:23.250 --> 39:24.490
Hello.

39:26.540 --> 39:27.416
Hello.

39:34.540 --> 39:35.450
[Levi] Hello.

39:35.460 --> 39:36.495
What?

39:36.500 --> 39:38.286
That look.

39:39.540 --> 39:41.451
[Levi] Hello.

39:41.460 --> 39:43.246
I just wanted
to say, um...

39:43.250 --> 39:44.615
[Levi] Hello.

39:44.620 --> 39:46.417
I know how hard
it's been for you.

39:48.670 --> 39:49.614
Dealing with Ryn
and the song.

39:49.620 --> 39:51.247
[hisses]

39:51.250 --> 39:54.071
I also know you're
trying to get better.

39:54.080 --> 39:56.412
My mom told me about
the support group meeting.

39:58.620 --> 39:59.871
She was there?

40:01.460 --> 40:03.496
Were you there
because of Ryn?

40:05.250 --> 40:07.036
Yeah.

40:07.040 --> 40:09.497
I think it's great
you're working on it.

40:12.750 --> 40:14.240
Means a lot.

40:17.460 --> 40:19.280
[footsteps]

40:21.920 --> 40:23.569
Still hungry.

40:23.580 --> 40:25.207
Never stop eating.

40:26.670 --> 40:28.615
When are you gonna tell her

40:28.620 --> 40:30.201
about what happened
to her mother?

40:30.210 --> 40:32.280
She cannot know this now.

40:33.710 --> 40:36.531
That humans did this.

40:36.540 --> 40:38.417
Or she will not stay on land.

40:40.540 --> 40:41.609
[sighs]

40:48.670 --> 40:50.615
It is a good day.

40:55.500 --> 40:58.663
[hissing breaths]

41:08.790 --> 41:11.076
[hissing breaths]

41:17.420 --> 41:18.489
[hisses]

41:19.880 --> 41:21.495
[grunting]

41:23.790 --> 41:26.873
[hissing]

41:31.670 --> 41:34.321
[placid high-pitched call]

41:37.210 --> 41:39.952
[music playing]
